{
  "texts": [
    "This research aims to explore the factors influencing public sentiment toward generative AI, examining both the positive impacts and the risks associated with these technologies.",
    "By understanding the public's views on the societal and ethical implications, this study seeks to contribute to the broader discussion on AI adoption and regulation.",
    "• Investigate the level of awareness among the general public regarding generative Al technologies.",
    "• Examine public attitudes towards the ethical implications of generative Al, such as its potential impact on employment, creativity, and privacy.",
    "• Understand the extent to which individuals believe that generative Al technologies like ChatGPT can positively or negatively impact society."
  ]
}